OL,7,FWATCH: ITV Meridian's Wesley Smith has
OL,8,Fbeen talking to the council about the
OL,9,Fpotential day centre closures.
OL,11,FWest Berkshire Council has said it
OL,12,Fguarantees that quality of care for
OL,13,Fvulnerable people will be maintained,
OL,14,Feven though there's a risk that three
OL,15,Fday centres they use will have to
OL,16,Fclose.
