OL,3,CCouncil vows day centre cuts will not
OL,4,Chappen until quality alternative is
OL,5,Cfound
OL,7,FGreenfield House in Calcot, Hungerford
OL,8,FResource Centre and The Phoenix Centre
OL,9,Fin Newbury are earmarked to close, as
OL,10,Fthe council aims to save #470,000 this
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FPlans to close the centres, which are
OL,14,Fused by vulnerable and disabled
OL,15,Fpeople, have left its users uncertain
OL,16,Fand worried about the future.
OL,18,FITV News Meridian spoke one family,
OL,19,Fwho could be affected in February 2025.
