OL,3,CCouncil vows day centre cuts will not
OL,4,Chappen until quality alternative is
OL,5,Cfound
OL,7,FPaul Coe, who is the Executive
OL,8,FDirector for Adult Social Care and
OL,9,FPublic Health at West Berkshire
OL,10,FCouncil, insists that the authority
OL,11,Fwill not close three day centres until
OL,12,Falternative funding of the same
OL,13,Fquality is found.
OL,15,FHe says that it's cheaper for the
OL,16,Fcouncil to outsource provision to
OL,17,Fcharities and care providers, than for
OL,18,Fthe authority to be the sole provider.
