OL,3,CCouncil vows day centre cuts will not
OL,4,Chappen until quality alternative is
OL,5,Cfound
OL,7,FPaul said: "There is a number of
OL,8,Fcomplicated reasons why it is often
OL,9,Fmore expensive for councils to do it
OL,10,Fourselves.
OL,12,F"You will see it all across the
OL,13,Fcountry that other local authorities
OL,14,Fhave withdrawn from the provider
OL,15,Fmarket entirely some time ago."
OL,17,FPaul Coe has said he takes personal
OL,18,Fresponsibility to make sure people's
OL,19,Fcare needs are met.
