OL,4,Chappen until quality alternative is
OL,5,Cfound
OL,7,FHe said: "I completely understand
OL,8,Fwhere it is coming from but where we
OL,9,Fhave assessed that someone has care
OL,10,Fneeds.
OL,12,F"There are different ways that we can
OL,13,Fmeet needs, but I do want to reassure
OL,14,Fpeople that there will not be a sudden
OL,15,Fceasing of services."
OL,17,FWest Berkshire Council insists it has
OL,18,Fto look at all options and will have
OL,19,Fto look elsewhere to make savings if
OL,20,Fthe quality threshold can't be met.
